{"lastModified":1771603061335,"uri":"c::9974682422::vessel::43a64960-ae2c-11ef-8d3c-397efb44f347","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Mykonos, Greece\n\nEnjoy this supremely versatile dayboat with a stylish walkaround centre cockpit and an inviting cabin, all with blistering pace and manoeuvrability thanks to her balanced, deep-V hull form developed by Wally and Ferretti Group's engineering department.\n\nVersatility is the superpower of the wallytender 43, perfectly united with Wally's sharp aesthetics and performance. Family day boat, superyscht tender or resort shuttle - the wallytender 43 fulfils each role with inimitable style. An armoury of accessories makes it simle for thw shipyard to switch the yacht smoothly from one location to another.\n\nAt the heart of the wallytender 43 lies its innovative centre cockpit design. This offers optimum protection for guests, even at the blistering 40-knots tio speed, with the convenience of a walkaround. Choice is all. Enjoy the freedom of the foredeck sunlounge, or find dappled shade beneath Wally's unique carbon sailcloth hard-top, witch appears to float on a single set of slim-line pillars. Enlarge your playground by folding down the two aft wings. Relax on extending sunpads, or on Wally's smart articulated dual sofa- sunpad.\n\nBelow deck, the wallytender 43 offers a double berth for unexpected overnighters or a quick nap. The space is naturally air conditioned and complemented by a generous bathroom with separate walk-in shower.\n\nThis dayboat is really about open-air living, power and is second to none.","blueprint":{"name":"WALLY 43","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::43a64960-ae2c-11ef-8d3c-397efb44f347::assets::acb08440-ae2f-11ef-b327-fdafbcfb39c0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::43a64960-ae2c-11ef-8d3c-397efb44f347::assets::acabf060-ae2f-11ef-b325-fdafbcfb39c0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::43a64960-ae2c-11ef-8d3c-397efb44f347::assets::acb195b0-ae2f-11e